character.name: cirucci sanderwicci
character.personality: Cirucci is rather rude, cocky and blunt. She scoffs at her opponents constantly, and slightly sadistic. However, she has no qualms about pointing out when others have similar traits

anime.name: Bleach
anime.quote: Would you mind not attacking me while I'm in the middle of saying something? Jeez, you have no manners, do you, four eyes?!
